content: अलक्षण {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Having no signs or marks. {@--2@} Having no characteristic or distinguishing marks; undefined, undistinguished; <ls>Ms. 1. 5.</ls> {@--3@} Having no good marks, inauspicious, unfortunate, ill-omened; क्लेशावहा भर्तुरलक्षणाहम् <ls>R. 14. 5.</ls> --णं {@--1@} A bad or inauspicious sign; <ls>Ms. 4. 156.</ls> {@--2@} That which is no definition, a bad definition.
